{
  "stem": "15962.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But slightly better, I couldn't tell you now what that meant.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At that time, we did not.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "As the-- then-- as I said, then there were women who were selected for work, and shipped out to another camp in Birkenau for temporary storage or holding.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] It must have been a very difficult decision, in retrospect, for mothers, whether they should abandon their children or face certain death by staying behind.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] When all the able-bodied men and women were selected and left the camp, only small children, mothers with children, and sick people were left behind.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Elderly and sick people.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I was [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] suddenly notified-- and I don't remember how-- that a-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] one of the officers, SS officers, decided that it would be a good idea to have a large group of young boys chosen for lighter works in the camp, in the camp itself, in Birkenau-Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 55
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was during the day, and we were [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] asked to strip in the same barrack that we were sort of during the day normally playing.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And had to-- I think we had to stand on a bench and he would look us over and decide sort of with a little whip whether we were OK or whether we should stay in the camp.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this happened-- we had to do that twice.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "First, he did it once.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then either we were too many that he selected, went through it again.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I was amongst those that were in the group that was immediately shipped out of the camp to another camp, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] two camps over.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Which was the man's camp, [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
